snippet.title: Smash Bash Crash Trailer
snippet.description:
Smash Bash Crash is a new couch side local multiplayer last one standing smash em up car game in which you compete with up to 4 real (or AI) players using nothing but your pimped out car and its awesome array of weaponry. Smash Bash Crash features 12 out there levels and multiple vehicles with an array of sick paintjobs, explosive weapons and a ripping soundtrack.

Visit www.smashbashcrash.com.au for more information.

Available now on Steam
